text: Navajo Nation resolve can be lesson to all. Hit damn hard, but banding together as community. Best outcomes ult. where leadership & citizenry align. Navajo will beat COVID-19 w/ or w/o us. Shame on us if not WITH. & must be said, White House sent NN suppmtl.30k test kits this wk.
